            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>The Future of the Negro</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"What a confession is this that after the war the status of the negro will
                    be determined!--So the war which was 'to settle the negro question,' affords no
                    settlement at all."</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Criticizes a Republican newspaper for stating that the post-war demand for
